    <body>
    <p>An <ph keyref="product"/>
      <xref keyref="glossentry_perspective"><term>perspective</term></xref> is an interface layout
      geared towards a specific use. The <ph keyref="product"/> interface uses standard interface
      <?oxy_comment_start author="George Bina" timestamp="20180904T150933+0000" comment="test"?>conventions<?oxy_comment_end?>
      and components to provide a familiar and intuitive
      <?oxy_delete author="George Bina" timestamp="20180904T150920+0000" content="editing"?>
      environment <?oxy_insert_start author="George Bina" timestamp="20180904T150923+0000"?>add
      <?oxy_insert_end?>across all operating systems. There are several <term>perspectives</term>
      that you can use to work with documents in <ph keyref="product"/>. You can change the
        <term>perspective</term>
      <ph product="author developer editor">by selecting the respective icon (<image
          href="../img/persp_icons.png" product="developer editor"/><image
          href="../img/persp_icons_author.png" product="author"/>) in the top-right corner of <ph
          keyref="product"/> or </ph>by selecting the <term>perspective</term> from the <menucascade>
        <uicontrol>Window</uicontrol>
        <uicontrol>Open Perspective</uicontrol>
      </menucascade> menu.</p>
